# linux-backup

A snapshot-based backup solution for linux systems.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Usage: backup [OPTIONS]

OPTIONS:
-h, --help                      This help
-t TYPE, --type TYPE            Where TYPE = [ full | inc ]

With -t inc:

It creates incremental backups from a list of source folders to a defined target folder under '/inc'. It compresses and archives monthly and anual backups under '/full'. 

With -t full

It creates a compressed single backupfrom a list of source folders to a defined target folder under '/full'.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
